race.description: Frankston Sand Soil & Mini Mix Bm70 Handicap
race.comment: REWARDS AND MORE (1) resumes having won two in a row at Ballarat Synthetic before a spell, scoring at $1.65 when last seen. No issue onto turf here having trialled well leading in and is suited at this trip. Looks a key chance. MADAME MASERATI (6) resumes. Her two failures before a spell were in much harder company but she won three on the bounce prior and is right up to winning this. She'll likely give them a start but can be rattling home. SOJU (10) resumes. She can mix her form but is a 1000m specialist and her best is good enough. PANO'S PRIDE (2) resumes and can kick up from the inside to take catching.
